Wyndham Hotels & Resorts makes travel possible for all. From big cities and small towns to beachfront resorts and highway hotels, our 25 brands bring a diverse perspective to the travel experience. With friendly service, thoughtful amenities, and a range of options for the everyday traveler, Wyndham will be there to welcome you wherever you go. See Our Locations OUR BRANDS See You on the Road With thousands of convenient locations across North America, Super 8 is a companion on the road that leaves travelers refueled for their journey ahead. LEARN MORE Seize the Days A bright take on travel, Days Inn focuses on the little things that surprise and delight guests to help them enjoy their stay and seize the days. LEARN MORE Say Hello to Red Boasting hundreds of locations worldwide, Ramada features a range of globally diverse properties for travelers looking for both full-service stays and quick stopovers. Learn More Wake up on the Bright Side With free daily breakfast, signature pillow-top mattresses, and contemporary rooms, La Quinta and LQ Hotel® locations are the bright spots in your travel journey. LEARN MORE Go Happy. Go HoJo. For guests looking for dependable accommodations, Howard Johnson delivers a warm, friendly experience every visit—just like they’ve been doing for decades. LEARN MORE Travelarge From hiking trips to beach vacations, Travelodge offers an ideal stay for travelers looking to start great adventures with an even better night’s sleep. LEARN MORE In Pursuit of Genuine Hospitality Built on genuine hospitality, AmericInn treats its guests like neighbors with comfortable guest rooms, cozy lobbies, and homestyle breakfast served every morning. LEARN MORE Relax, You’re Here Conveniently situated in key airport and suburban locations, Wyndham Garden offers thoughtful guest rooms, cozy lounges, and flexible meeting spaces to make your travels a bit easier. LEARN MORE Stay in Our Hometown Offering great value and friendly service, Baymont brings the comforts of home to its guests with inviting rooms, useful amenities, and free breakfast. LEARN MORE Microtel Just Makes Sense With modern rooms and award-winning service, Microtel provides a consistent, seamless stay designed to give guests an affordable hotel experience. LEARN MORE Let’s Connect Featuring oversized guest rooms and essential amenities, Wingate creates a relaxed environment that keeps guests connected, productive, and on schedule while traveling. LEARN MORE Stay Longer, Stay Better Featuring spacious suites with fully equipped kitchens, free WiFi, and free hot breakfast, Hawthorn Extended Stay offers a welcoming atmosphere that’s perfect for extended stays. LEARN MORE Leave Your Mark A collection of unique independent hotels, Trademark Collection celebrates the individuality of each of its properties and enables guests to experience every destination on their own terms. LEARN MORE Powered by the City Tucked in the heart of the world's greatest cities, TRYP is on the pulse of the best local hotspots and must-see sights—putting everything you need right at your fingertips. LEARN MORE Simply Comfortable Located in popular business and vacation destinations, Wyndham hotels feature smartly designed guest rooms and thoughtful amenities that make for a comfortable stay. LEARN MORE Be the Protagonist From sophisticated designs to world-class amenities, Esplendor hotels magnificently blend comfort and style in remarkable Latin American locations. LEARN MORE Thinking Like You Featuring sleek décor and attentive service, Dazzler hotels are centrally located in some of the most vibrant neighborhoods in Latin America and offer easy access to top attractions. LEARN MORE FUEL YOUR WANDERLUST Situated in some of Europe’s most exciting cities, Vienna House inspires guests to discover new destinations and find fun wherever they go with cool-yet-comfortable spaces and superior service. LEARN MORE Inspire Discovery Creating inspiring environments that bring people together, Dolce Hotels and Resorts offer incredible locations and state-of-the-art meeting spaces for guests to connect and discover. LEARN MORE You’ve Arrived Delivering incredible experiences in spectacular destinations, Registry Collection Hotels feature thoughtful design, brilliant service, and unsurpassed attention to detail. LEARN MORE Distinctive Experiences With attentive service, relaxing surroundings, and unique touches, Wyndham Grand creates authentic, one-of-a-kind experiences in exceptional destinations around the world. LEARN MORE Go All In From exciting eats and refreshing cocktails to live entertainment and non-stop activities, Wyndham Alltra delivers the ultimate all-inclusive experience for all. LEARN MORE LONGER STAYS READY FOR YOU Intentionally created to help you settle in, ECHO Suites Extended Stay features thoughtfully designed accommodations and everyday essentials—from kitchens with cooktops and full-size refrigerators to smart TVs and free WiFi. LEARN MORE SUITES THAT FEEL LIKE HOME Offering sleek furnished suites with washers and dryers, full kitchens, and cozy living areas, WaterWalk Extended Stay provides the perfect space to settle in, stretch out, and stay awhile.
